description: Acoustic guitar classes for complete beginners. You’ll learn basic chords, strumming patterns, and how to play simple songs from day one.
Conversational English sessions for non-native speakers. Focus on fluency, pronunciation, and real-life speaking scenarios.
Learn HTML, CSS, and basic JavaScript by building simple landing pages and interactive components from scratch.
One-on-one sessions to help you plan your day, set priorities, and build habits using simple tools like Notion and Google Calendar.

Learn how to set up a complete Shopify store from scratch. We’ll cover choosing a theme, adding products, setting up payments and shipping, and configuring essential apps. By the end, you’ll have a fully functional basic online store ready to share with customers.
Quick and easy recipes for students and beginners: one-pot meals, simple curries, and budget-friendly lunch ideas.
Understand user-centered design, wireframing, and basic prototyping using Figma. Perfect for beginners entering UI/UX.
Hands-on Python basics: variables, loops, functions, and small practice problems to build a strong foundation.
